  ;; PROBLEM 1: The role-based reanalysis is structurally disconnected
  ;;
  ;; It appears in:
  ;;   - Methods 3.4 (described as "fifth analytical stage")
  ;;   - Section 4.2 one paragraph (coordination complexity)
